WEBVTT

00:00:10.833 --> 00:00:12.500
[snoring]

00:00:12.542 --> 00:00:14.792
[horse whinnies]

00:00:14.833 --> 00:00:16.833
[sighs]

00:00:19.333 --> 00:00:20.542
[KAZUMA]
This ain't worth it.

00:00:22.250 --> 00:00:25.958
Workin' all day for peanuts.
Dealing with a loser goddess.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:28.042
Fantasy world, my ass!

00:00:28.083 --> 00:00:29.958
This ain't the life
I signed up for!

00:00:30.958 --> 00:00:32.458
What happened
to fighting dragons

00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:34.542
with a kick-ass magic sword?

00:00:34.583 --> 00:00:37.000
And being the edgy hero
everyone's been waiting for?

00:00:38.042 --> 00:00:41.458
Where's the party member I'm
supposed to fall in love with?

00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:43.917
This place is such a rip-off!

00:00:46.500 --> 00:00:48.708
[GIRLS]
Red rover, red rover!

00:00:48.750 --> 00:00:49.667
[thumps]

00:00:49.708 --> 00:00:51.250
[AQUA]
I hate being broke!

00:00:51.292 --> 00:00:53.250
I can't live like a pauper!

00:00:53.292 --> 00:00:54.667
That does it!

00:00:54.708 --> 00:00:56.792
Let's do a quest!
I don't care what!

00:00:56.833 --> 00:00:58.333
I don't care if it's hard!

00:00:58.375 --> 00:01:00.083
I want money!

00:01:00.125 --> 00:01:03.500
Well, I would not mind
a hard quest.

00:01:03.542 --> 00:01:05.500
Please, let's go
on a quest!

00:01:05.542 --> 00:01:07.833
I'm sick of working
a part-time job!

00:01:07.875 --> 00:01:10.458
The boss yells at me if I
don't sell all the croquettes!

00:01:10.500 --> 00:01:14.667
I promise I won't slack off!
I'll be a good party member!

00:01:14.708 --> 00:01:17.667
[KAZUMA] How can a goddess
be so pathetic?!

00:01:17.708 --> 00:01:20.792
Look, sooner or later,
I'm gonna run out of money, too.

00:01:20.833 --> 00:01:23.542
So what the heck, pick out
a quest and we'll go with you.

00:01:23.583 --> 00:01:24.875
Yes, sir!

00:01:24.917 --> 00:01:25.875
[giggling]

00:01:27.708 --> 00:01:29.958
I can't believe
you're letting her choose.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:32.375
I get the feeling she'll pick
something horrific.

00:01:32.417 --> 00:01:35.292
I definitely would not mind
a quest like that!

00:01:35.333 --> 00:01:38.000
Mmm? Mmm?

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:41.083
-This one.
-Hold your horses!

00:01:41.125 --> 00:01:43.333
I wanna see what kinda crap
you picked first!

00:01:43.375 --> 00:01:44.875
[muffled screaming]

00:01:44.917 --> 00:01:47.833
"A manticore and a griffin
are fighting over territory

00:01:47.875 --> 00:01:49.958
"in the region
and disturbing the peace.

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:51.708
"If you kill them,
you will receive a reward

00:01:51.750 --> 00:01:53.333
of five hundred thousand eris."

00:01:53.375 --> 00:01:55.292
Are you out of your mind?!

00:01:55.333 --> 00:01:57.625
It's a good thing I came over
to check on her.

00:01:57.667 --> 00:01:58.833
She was on her way
to picking

00:01:58.875 --> 00:02:00.917
the gnarliest quest
on the board!

00:02:00.958 --> 00:02:02.542
[AQUA]
Ooh! How about this one?

00:02:03.667 --> 00:02:05.708
"Need to purify
the town's lake.

00:02:05.750 --> 00:02:08.125
"It has become so foul,
no one can drink from it

00:02:08.167 --> 00:02:10.542
"and brutal alligators
have made it their home.

00:02:10.583 --> 00:02:12.833
"The monsters will leave
once it has been purified,

00:02:12.875 --> 00:02:14.208
"so you won't have
to kill them.

00:02:14.250 --> 00:02:16.458
Three hundred thousand
eris reward."

00:02:16.500 --> 00:02:19.000
Three hundred thousand?!

00:02:19.042 --> 00:02:21.250
This one's got my name
written all over it!

00:03:55.250 --> 00:03:57.208
Uh, huh?

00:03:57.250 --> 00:03:58.375
Uh...

00:03:59.417 --> 00:04:00.500
How about it?

00:04:00.542 --> 00:04:03.000
Hold on,
you can purify water?

00:04:03.042 --> 00:04:04.333
Are you kidding?

00:04:04.375 --> 00:04:06.708
You silly boy,
who do you think I am?

00:04:06.750 --> 00:04:08.375
I can't believe
I have to tell you.

00:04:08.417 --> 00:04:10.250
With my name and looks,
it should be obvious

00:04:10.292 --> 00:04:11.375
what I'm a goddess of!

00:04:11.417 --> 00:04:13.250
The goddess
of cheap party tricks?

00:04:13.292 --> 00:04:14.750
No, you stupid shut-in NEET!

00:04:14.792 --> 00:04:16.042
Are you blind?!

00:04:16.083 --> 00:04:17.583
My eyes are blue,
my hair's blue!

00:04:17.625 --> 00:04:19.292
I'm the goddess of water!

00:04:19.333 --> 00:04:21.625
Alright, fine, we'll take it.

00:04:21.667 --> 00:04:22.750
Better yet, you take it,

00:04:22.792 --> 00:04:24.500
and that way,
the reward's all yours.

00:04:24.542 --> 00:04:26.375
Oh!
[nervous chuckle]

00:04:27.375 --> 00:04:29.542
I'm pretty sure
the monsters will attack me

00:04:29.583 --> 00:04:31.500
while I'm purifying, so...

00:04:31.542 --> 00:04:34.542
...I sort of need
your guys' protection?

00:04:34.583 --> 00:04:36.167
[KAZUMA]
Mm-hmm.

00:04:37.167 --> 00:04:39.792
How long does it take?
Five minutes?

00:04:39.833 --> 00:04:42.042
Hmm.

00:04:42.083 --> 00:04:44.042
-More like half a day.
-No, thank you!

00:04:44.083 --> 00:04:47.042
Please, please, please, Kazuma!
Help me out here!

00:04:47.083 --> 00:04:48.417
I really, really need this!

00:04:48.458 --> 00:04:50.917
How do you purify
a lake, anyway?!

00:04:50.958 --> 00:04:52.250
Huh?

00:04:52.292 --> 00:04:55.083
Well, um,
I'm a high-level goddess.

00:04:55.125 --> 00:04:56.625
All I have to do
is touch the water,

00:04:56.667 --> 00:04:58.833
and that should do the trick.

00:04:58.875 --> 00:04:59.833
That's it, huh?

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:02.208
You know what?

00:05:02.250 --> 00:05:03.625
I think I know how
to keep you safe

00:05:03.667 --> 00:05:05.292
from the monsters
while you do it.

00:05:05.333 --> 00:05:06.167
How?

00:05:07.292 --> 00:05:08.417
[LUNA]
Konosuba!

00:05:15.333 --> 00:05:17.750
Are you sure about this?

00:05:17.792 --> 00:05:20.500
What are you worried about?
You're perfectly safe in there.

00:05:20.542 --> 00:05:22.292
Don't tell me
you're getting cold feet now.

00:05:23.333 --> 00:05:24.833
No, I'm not.

00:05:24.875 --> 00:05:27.042
I just feel like
some rare monster

00:05:27.083 --> 00:05:29.542
that's being carted off
to the circus.

00:05:35.083 --> 00:05:37.042
[owl hooting]

00:05:42.667 --> 00:05:43.958
[KAZUMA]
I know how it looks,

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:45.792
but no,
we're not gonna ditch her.

00:05:45.833 --> 00:05:47.708
This was to keep her safe.

00:05:47.750 --> 00:05:49.583
See, this way,
she could touch the water

00:05:49.625 --> 00:05:51.833
and purify it
from inside the cage.

00:05:51.875 --> 00:05:54.667
Aqua!
If you need help, holler!

00:05:54.708 --> 00:05:57.042
We'll reel you in,
cage and all!

00:05:57.083 --> 00:05:58.333
I hate this.

00:05:58.375 --> 00:06:00.167
Now I know
how a teabag feels

00:06:00.208 --> 00:06:02.583
after it's been steeping
for too long.

00:06:06.625 --> 00:06:10.000
That iron bar makes
three hundred and twelve.

00:06:10.042 --> 00:06:12.333
That iron bar makes
three hundred thirteen.

00:06:12.375 --> 00:06:14.792
No monsters have appeared yet.

00:06:14.833 --> 00:06:16.750
I noticed that, too.

00:06:16.792 --> 00:06:18.542
Well, I noticed
you're more chill today

00:06:18.583 --> 00:06:19.917
than you normally are.

00:06:19.958 --> 00:06:21.292
What?

00:06:21.333 --> 00:06:23.500
Usually, you'd brag about
how scary your power is,

00:06:23.542 --> 00:06:25.625
then blow the damn lake
to smithereens.

00:06:25.667 --> 00:06:26.833
He's right. You would.

00:06:26.875 --> 00:06:28.542
I-is that what
you think of me?!

00:06:28.583 --> 00:06:29.833
That I'm that immature?!

00:06:31.375 --> 00:06:33.375
I wouldn't dare waste
my fearsome spell

00:06:33.417 --> 00:06:36.125
on mere alligators,
it is far too precious!

00:06:36.167 --> 00:06:38.958
You got no problem usin' it
on everything else.

00:06:40.083 --> 00:06:42.458
Aqua! You good?

00:06:42.500 --> 00:06:45.625
How's that purifying
comin' along?

00:06:45.667 --> 00:06:47.917
Going well, thank you!

00:06:47.958 --> 00:06:50.875
[KAZUMA] You'll catch cold if
you sit in that water too long!

00:06:50.917 --> 00:06:53.417
You need to get out
to go pee or anything?

00:06:53.458 --> 00:06:56.417
I'm an arch-priest!
We don't "go pee or anything!"

00:06:56.458 --> 00:06:58.708
She sounds like
she's doing just fine.

00:06:58.750 --> 00:07:01.625
By the way, Crimson Demons
don't pee or anything either.

00:07:01.667 --> 00:07:03.958
What, are you guys like robots
or something?

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:04.875
A-actually,

00:07:06.042 --> 00:07:08.000
I-I am a crusader.

00:07:08.042 --> 00:07:10.417
We don't--
Such things are not--

00:07:10.458 --> 00:07:11.875
[straining]

00:07:11.917 --> 00:07:15.083
Please. Stop.
You're not convincing me at all.

00:07:15.125 --> 00:07:16.875
And as for you
and the soggy blue one,

00:07:16.917 --> 00:07:18.333
let's put you to the test.

00:07:18.375 --> 00:07:19.708
After we're done here,
we'll do a quest

00:07:19.750 --> 00:07:21.083
that takes longer
than a day,

00:07:21.125 --> 00:07:22.833
one with lots of walking.

00:07:22.875 --> 00:07:24.750
No, anything but that!

00:07:24.792 --> 00:07:27.375
N-not because
Crimson Demons have to pee!

00:07:27.417 --> 00:07:29.500
We just hate long quests
is all.

00:07:29.542 --> 00:07:32.000
You are even more sadistic
than I hoped!

00:07:33.583 --> 00:07:35.833
The alligators
still haven't shown up.

00:07:35.875 --> 00:07:37.458
It would be great
if we could finish this

00:07:37.500 --> 00:07:39.042
without having to fight them.

00:07:39.083 --> 00:07:41.750
Shut up! You wanna trigger
a flag or something?!

00:07:41.792 --> 00:07:43.750
[AQUA] [whimpering]
K-Kazuma?!

00:07:43.792 --> 00:07:45.125
Something's coming!

00:07:45.167 --> 00:07:46.750
A lot of somethings
are coming!

00:07:46.792 --> 00:07:48.500
[screaming]

00:07:48.542 --> 00:07:50.500
Kazuma! Kazuma!

00:07:50.542 --> 00:07:52.750
[crying]

00:07:54.583 --> 00:07:55.875
[AQUA] [screaming]
KonoSuba!

00:07:59.667 --> 00:08:01.667
[KAZUMA] Before the gators,
Aqua just sat there

00:08:01.708 --> 00:08:04.750
thinking her goddess-y butt
was enough to purify the lake.

00:08:04.792 --> 00:08:06.750
She was being
more proactive now.

00:08:06.792 --> 00:08:08.750
[AQUA]
Purification! Purification!

00:08:08.792 --> 00:08:11.583
Purification! Purification!
Purifica--

00:08:11.625 --> 00:08:14.042
-[thudding]
-[screaming]

00:08:14.083 --> 00:08:16.000
Purification! Purification!

00:08:16.042 --> 00:08:19.667
Purification! Purification!
Purification!

00:08:20.708 --> 00:08:21.833
What was that?!

00:08:21.875 --> 00:08:23.542
The cage just made
a really weird sound!

00:08:23.583 --> 00:08:26.875
Aqua! You wanna
call it a day?

00:08:26.917 --> 00:08:29.667
Say the word and we'll come
down and reel you in!

00:08:29.708 --> 00:08:33.667
No! If I give up now,
I won't get the reward!

00:08:33.708 --> 00:08:36.375
-[crunch]
-[crying, screaming]

00:08:36.417 --> 00:08:38.083
The cage just made
a crunch sound!

00:08:38.125 --> 00:08:40.333
Cages aren't supposed
to go "crunch"!

00:08:41.417 --> 00:08:42.792
Purification! Purification!

00:08:42.833 --> 00:08:47.292
I'm feeling jealous.
It looks fun inside that cage.

00:08:47.333 --> 00:08:48.250
Down, girl.

00:08:48.292 --> 00:08:50.250
Purification! Purification!

00:08:50.292 --> 00:08:52.750
Purification! Purification!

00:08:52.792 --> 00:08:54.708
Purification!

00:08:59.250 --> 00:09:03.292
[water sloshing]

00:09:07.292 --> 00:09:09.583
[MEGUMIN] Well, the lake
seems to be purified.

00:09:09.625 --> 00:09:11.750
The alligators have left
the area, too.

00:09:11.792 --> 00:09:13.500
You okay in there, Aqua?

00:09:14.792 --> 00:09:16.083
A-Aqua?

00:09:16.125 --> 00:09:17.292
[KAZUMA]
Hey, Aqua.

00:09:17.333 --> 00:09:18.667
Lady Aqua!

00:09:19.667 --> 00:09:21.208
Hey!

00:09:21.250 --> 00:09:23.458
Come on, say something!
You hurt?!

00:09:25.250 --> 00:09:26.958
-[sobbing]
-[grunts]

00:09:27.000 --> 00:09:29.042
If those stupid gators
freaked you out that much,

00:09:29.083 --> 00:09:31.042
you should have quit
the quest.

00:09:31.083 --> 00:09:33.792
Come on now.
Let's go home.

00:09:33.833 --> 00:09:36.708
Hey, guess what.
We were talkin' and...

00:09:36.750 --> 00:09:39.375
...well, we decided you can have
the reward for this.

00:09:39.417 --> 00:09:40.625
That's right, Aqua.

00:09:40.667 --> 00:09:42.208
You can keep
the three hundred thousand eris

00:09:42.250 --> 00:09:43.250
all to yourself.

00:09:43.292 --> 00:09:44.583
I-it's only fair!

00:09:44.625 --> 00:09:45.917
After all,
you were the one

00:09:45.958 --> 00:09:46.917
who did all the work.

00:09:48.458 --> 00:09:51.250
Y-you can come on out now,
it's safe.

00:09:51.292 --> 00:09:53.417
The gators are all gone,
promise.

00:09:53.458 --> 00:09:55.458
[AQUA] I'll stay in the cage,
thank you.

00:09:55.500 --> 00:09:56.417
Seriously?

00:09:57.708 --> 00:10:00.792
The world is too big.
Too scary.

00:10:00.833 --> 00:10:02.750
I will never leave
this cage again.

00:10:06.042 --> 00:10:08.583
[KAZUMA]
Aqua's been traumatized again.

00:10:08.625 --> 00:10:10.583
Man, these quests
are tough on her.

00:10:22.792 --> 00:10:23.875
[whooshing]

00:10:23.917 --> 00:10:25.625
[explosion booms]

00:10:27.125 --> 00:10:29.333
[growling]

00:10:29.375 --> 00:10:31.583
It's the legendary
Ancient Dragon!

00:10:31.625 --> 00:10:33.250
Can we even beat that thing?

00:10:34.292 --> 00:10:35.875
Maybe we should get
out of here!

00:10:37.708 --> 00:10:39.750
My name is Kyouya Mitsurugi.

00:10:39.792 --> 00:10:42.542
When I was alive,
I was an ordinary high schooler.

00:10:42.583 --> 00:10:45.083
But after I died,
I met a beautiful goddess,

00:10:45.125 --> 00:10:47.875
who reincarnated me
into this world as its hero.

00:10:48.875 --> 00:10:50.375
If we don't deal
with this now,

00:10:50.417 --> 00:10:52.250
it will ravage the land

00:10:52.292 --> 00:10:54.708
and kill everything
in its path!

00:10:54.750 --> 00:10:56.500
We're the only ones
who can stop it.

00:10:57.500 --> 00:10:59.125
And stop it we shall!

00:10:59.167 --> 00:11:00.375
[BOTH]
Kyouya!

00:11:00.417 --> 00:11:02.875
[GIRL 1] They say
the gods forged his sword,

00:11:02.917 --> 00:11:04.292
and only he can use it!

00:11:04.333 --> 00:11:06.375
[GIRL 2]
The magic sword Gram!

00:11:06.417 --> 00:11:09.208
[yelling]

00:11:09.250 --> 00:11:10.958
[explosion booms]

00:11:16.250 --> 00:11:18.542
[crow cawing]

00:11:18.583 --> 00:11:20.583
[GIRL 1]
Yup! That's my Kyouya!

00:11:20.625 --> 00:11:23.417
It only took him one blow
to kill the Ancient Dragon!

00:11:23.458 --> 00:11:25.750
Wait, since when
did he become your Kyouya?!

00:11:25.792 --> 00:11:27.750
Wait, ladies,
please don't fight!

00:11:29.000 --> 00:11:30.500
[GIRL 1]
He's mine and that's that!

00:11:30.542 --> 00:11:32.708
[GIRL 2] What are you talking
about?! He's mine, got it?!

00:11:32.750 --> 00:11:35.625
[KYOUYA] I swear,
I will save this world.

00:11:36.625 --> 00:11:38.500
I promised her I would.

00:11:40.375 --> 00:11:42.500
[AQUA]
Now, begin your journey

00:11:42.542 --> 00:11:46.042
in a new world
with Gram, the magic sword.

00:11:47.208 --> 00:11:48.542
Yes, m'lady.

00:11:48.583 --> 00:11:50.792
I swear I will slay
the Devil King

00:11:50.833 --> 00:11:52.042
and save the world for you.

00:11:53.042 --> 00:11:55.167
Go now, become its hero.

00:11:57.417 --> 00:12:00.625
[AQUA] [humming]
Doo doo doo-doo-doo.

00:12:00.667 --> 00:12:02.083
♪ Gaze upon this ♪

00:12:02.125 --> 00:12:04.958
[KYOUYA] I know that voice!
Could it be?!

00:12:05.000 --> 00:12:06.125
♪ Washed-up goddess ♪

00:12:06.167 --> 00:12:08.625
Hey, Kyouya,
where're you going?!

00:12:08.667 --> 00:12:10.542
-[AQUA] ♪ Of me ♪
-[KYOUYA panting]

00:12:12.042 --> 00:12:17.542
♪ Who will they sell me to? ♪

00:12:17.583 --> 00:12:22.042
♪ What's a girl
like me to do? ♪

00:12:23.583 --> 00:12:25.667
M'lady!

00:12:29.542 --> 00:12:31.917
♪ Who could they sell me to? ♪

00:12:31.958 --> 00:12:33.458
Aqua.

00:12:33.500 --> 00:12:36.500
Geez, would you quit
singin' that weird-ass song?

00:12:36.542 --> 00:12:37.667
Stop it already.

00:12:37.708 --> 00:12:38.875
Do you know
how bad this looks

00:12:38.917 --> 00:12:40.125
with you in there?

00:12:40.167 --> 00:12:42.958
Oh nice, everyone in town
is starin' at us.

00:12:43.000 --> 00:12:44.292
Would you get out already?!

00:12:45.458 --> 00:12:49.417
No. This cage is
my sanctuary now.

00:12:49.458 --> 00:12:52.792
It's too scary out there,
so I'll stay in here.

00:12:52.833 --> 00:12:55.792
Shutting herself off
from the world isn't healthy.

00:12:55.833 --> 00:12:57.500
No, it is not.

00:12:57.542 --> 00:12:59.250
She's just like
I used to be.

00:12:59.292 --> 00:13:01.542
-[MEGUMIN/DARKNESS] Huh?
-Never mind. Nothing.

00:13:01.583 --> 00:13:04.458
[KYOUYA] M'lady!
I'll get you out of there!

00:13:04.500 --> 00:13:06.292
-[grunting]
-[bars creaking]

00:13:07.333 --> 00:13:09.250
-Damn!
-Wow, he's strong!

00:13:09.292 --> 00:13:11.458
What are you doing
in this cage, m'lady?!

00:13:11.500 --> 00:13:12.792
-You're a goddess!
-[DARKNESS] Hey.

00:13:13.792 --> 00:13:16.500
My friend did not give you
permission to touch her.

00:13:16.542 --> 00:13:18.667
Who are you? Out with it!

00:13:19.792 --> 00:13:20.917
Do you know this guy?

00:13:20.958 --> 00:13:22.708
'Cause it sounds
like he knows you!

00:13:22.750 --> 00:13:24.667
He called you "goddess"!

00:13:24.708 --> 00:13:25.958
G-goddess?

00:13:26.000 --> 00:13:26.875
Yeah, just now!

00:13:29.417 --> 00:13:30.375
Hmm?

00:13:32.125 --> 00:13:34.417
That's right!
I am a goddess, huh!

00:13:34.458 --> 00:13:37.250
She forgot?!
Who forgets a thing like--

00:13:37.292 --> 00:13:38.167
Oh, right.

00:13:42.000 --> 00:13:44.167
[yelps]

00:13:45.875 --> 00:13:48.667
How can this goddess be
of service to you, good sir?

00:13:50.333 --> 00:13:51.333
Who are you?

00:13:51.375 --> 00:13:52.958
I-it's me, m'lady!

00:13:53.000 --> 00:13:54.250
Kyouya Mitsurugi!

00:13:54.292 --> 00:13:55.917
Don't you remember me?

00:13:55.958 --> 00:13:57.625
I died
and you reincarnated me

00:13:57.667 --> 00:14:00.167
and gave me Gram,
the magic sword?

00:14:00.208 --> 00:14:01.750
-Um...
-[gasps]

00:14:01.792 --> 00:14:03.000
Huh?

00:14:03.042 --> 00:14:07.167
Uh... Oh, right, right!
That guy!

00:14:07.208 --> 00:14:09.708
Sorry, I totally forgot
for a second there!

00:14:09.750 --> 00:14:11.542
I helped so many people
cross over,

00:14:11.583 --> 00:14:13.875
I was bound to forget
a few here and there!

00:14:13.917 --> 00:14:15.750
Uh, sure.

00:14:17.750 --> 00:14:19.917
It has been
a while, m'lady.

00:14:19.958 --> 00:14:22.042
And I'm fighting hard
to save this world.

00:14:22.083 --> 00:14:24.042
To be its hero.

00:14:24.083 --> 00:14:25.292
By the way,

00:14:25.333 --> 00:14:27.083
I hope you don't
mind me asking,

00:14:27.125 --> 00:14:29.667
but why were you in a cage?

00:14:29.708 --> 00:14:33.000
[KAZUMA] Oh, brother.
Where do I start?

00:14:33.042 --> 00:14:35.042
[AQUA/KAZUMA]
Ko-no-su-ba!

00:14:35.083 --> 00:14:36.542
KONOSUBA
What?!

00:14:36.583 --> 00:14:39.458
You dragged m'lady
to this world against her will?

00:14:39.500 --> 00:14:41.958
Then locked her in a cage
and dunked her in a lake?!

00:14:42.000 --> 00:14:44.583
You monster, how could you?!

00:14:44.625 --> 00:14:46.667
N-no, wait!
I don't really mind

00:14:46.708 --> 00:14:48.708
that he forced me
to come here anymore!

00:14:48.750 --> 00:14:51.458
I'm having lots of fun, doing
all sorts of life-y things!

00:14:51.500 --> 00:14:52.917
Please, m'lady.

00:14:52.958 --> 00:14:55.625
I don't know how this guy
influenced your judgment,

00:14:55.667 --> 00:14:57.667
but you're a goddess,
remember?!

00:14:57.708 --> 00:14:59.125
He's a nobody!

00:14:59.167 --> 00:15:01.417
[KAZUMA] Listen to this asswipe,
flappin' away.

00:15:01.458 --> 00:15:04.500
Hell, he doesn't even know
what Aqua's really like!

00:15:04.542 --> 00:15:05.708
What's up?

00:15:05.750 --> 00:15:07.083
[MAN] Two dudes
fightin' over some chick.

00:15:07.125 --> 00:15:09.250
[KYOUYA] If you don't mind
my asking, Lady Aqua,

00:15:09.292 --> 00:15:10.833
which inn are you staying at?

00:15:10.875 --> 00:15:13.708
It's not an inn.
It's the stables.

00:15:13.750 --> 00:15:15.333
Huh?

00:15:15.375 --> 00:15:16.833
-[growling]
-[DARKNESS] Hey!

00:15:16.875 --> 00:15:18.458
Take your hands
off him this instant!

00:15:18.500 --> 00:15:20.958
Is there no limit
to your rudeness?!

00:15:21.000 --> 00:15:23.167
I could end him
with an Explosion?

00:15:23.208 --> 00:15:25.208
[KAZUMA] Please don't.
You'll end me, too.

00:15:25.250 --> 00:15:27.292
Interesting.

00:15:27.333 --> 00:15:29.792
A crusader
and an arch-wizard.

00:15:29.833 --> 00:15:33.625
And charming ones at that,
if you don't mind me saying so.

00:15:33.667 --> 00:15:36.208
You're blessed to have such
excellent people as allies.

00:15:36.250 --> 00:15:39.125
And yet, you make Lady Aqua
sleep in a dirty stable.

00:15:39.167 --> 00:15:40.250
Have you no shame?!

00:15:43.417 --> 00:15:44.500
[KAZUMA]
Thanks to the magic sword

00:15:44.542 --> 00:15:46.625
this jackass got
when he reincarnated,

00:15:46.667 --> 00:15:48.333
I bet his life here's
been hassle-free

00:15:48.375 --> 00:15:50.583
and way easier than mine.

00:15:50.625 --> 00:15:52.792
I worked my way up from nothing
to get what I have,

00:15:52.833 --> 00:15:54.417
so for him to lecture me?

00:15:54.458 --> 00:15:56.667
He can go screw himself.

00:15:56.708 --> 00:15:58.500
And for him to call
these three "excellent"?

00:15:59.667 --> 00:16:01.167
Not once...

00:16:01.208 --> 00:16:02.667
...have I ever...

00:16:02.708 --> 00:16:04.375
...ever, ever...

00:16:04.417 --> 00:16:05.708
...seen these chicks...

00:16:05.750 --> 00:16:07.375
...be excellent!

00:16:07.417 --> 00:16:08.833
Look, ladies,

00:16:08.875 --> 00:16:10.000
I'm a sword-master

00:16:10.042 --> 00:16:11.792
and I'd love
to have you in my party.

00:16:11.833 --> 00:16:14.375
I'll treat you well,
and I'll buy you the best gear.

00:16:14.417 --> 00:16:16.000
[BOTH groan]

00:16:16.042 --> 00:16:18.375
This guy's trouble
with a capital "T."

00:16:18.417 --> 00:16:20.792
He's giving me the
heebie-jeebies something fierce.

00:16:20.833 --> 00:16:23.708
Like, he's so full
of himself, it's scary.

00:16:23.750 --> 00:16:27.042
Agreed. That man makes me feel
so conflicted.

00:16:27.083 --> 00:16:29.125
I enjoy being hit
more than attacking,

00:16:29.167 --> 00:16:32.042
but the urge to punch
his face is irresistible!

00:16:32.083 --> 00:16:35.042
I want to blow him up.
Let me blow him up.

00:16:35.083 --> 00:16:36.708
Well, you heard 'em.

00:16:36.750 --> 00:16:38.375
These excellent ladies
would rather stick

00:16:38.417 --> 00:16:41.083
with a nobody like me
than join you.

00:16:41.125 --> 00:16:42.083
Later, dude.

00:16:45.167 --> 00:16:46.417
-[KYOUYA] Wait!
-[groans]

00:16:46.458 --> 00:16:47.458
[cape flutters]

00:16:48.458 --> 00:16:50.042
You're blocking our way.

00:16:50.083 --> 00:16:52.500
I am sorry, but I can't leave
Lady Aqua

00:16:52.542 --> 00:16:54.417
in a party that mistreats her.

00:16:54.458 --> 00:16:57.042
[KAZUMA] He's the type
who can't seem to take a hint.

00:16:57.083 --> 00:16:59.333
I know
what's comin' up next.

00:17:00.375 --> 00:17:01.708
Let's spar for her.

00:17:01.750 --> 00:17:03.208
[KAZUMA]
Called it.

00:17:03.250 --> 00:17:06.250
If I beat you,
Lady Aqua comes with me.

00:17:06.292 --> 00:17:09.417
And if you beat me,
I'll grant you any one request.

00:17:09.458 --> 00:17:11.417
Okay, you're on,
ready-set-go!

00:17:11.458 --> 00:17:13.083
H-hold on a second!

00:17:13.125 --> 00:17:15.667
Steal!

00:17:19.458 --> 00:17:20.458
Huh?

00:17:21.458 --> 00:17:24.792
-[sword clangs]
-[groaning]

00:17:26.208 --> 00:17:28.833
That'll teach you
to open your big mouth.

00:17:28.875 --> 00:17:31.542
[GIRL 1]
Why, you coward!

00:17:31.583 --> 00:17:33.875
Coward, coward, coward!

00:17:35.625 --> 00:17:37.375
Let me guess,
you guys are with him, right?

00:17:37.417 --> 00:17:40.750
That's right, you jerk!
Y-you jerky coward!

00:17:40.792 --> 00:17:43.750
[KAZUMA] This doofus with
a magic sword challenged me,

00:17:43.792 --> 00:17:45.708
a noob adventurer
with weak gear,

00:17:45.750 --> 00:17:46.917
and I'm the cheater?!

00:17:46.958 --> 00:17:49.250
Give Gram back
to him right now!

00:17:49.292 --> 00:17:52.000
That's Kyouya's sword, and he's
the only one who can use it!

00:17:52.042 --> 00:17:54.125
Huh? For real?

00:17:54.167 --> 00:17:55.208
Yup, it's true.

00:17:55.250 --> 00:17:57.750
He's the only one
that can use Gram.

00:17:57.792 --> 00:17:59.833
Huh?

00:18:01.583 --> 00:18:03.583
Too bad, I won, it's mine.

00:18:03.625 --> 00:18:05.750
Wait! You can't just
walk off with it!

00:18:05.792 --> 00:18:07.833
You didn't win,
you took him off guard!

00:18:10.750 --> 00:18:12.125
[KAZUMA]
I believe everyone's equal,

00:18:12.167 --> 00:18:14.000
ladies and dudes.

00:18:14.042 --> 00:18:15.750
So, I don't have a problem
throwin' down

00:18:15.792 --> 00:18:18.750
on a couple of girls
if they're askin' for it.

00:18:18.792 --> 00:18:21.917
Right now,
you're asking for it.

00:18:21.958 --> 00:18:24.375
If I use Steal,
things could get embarrassing

00:18:24.417 --> 00:18:25.875
and drafty for you.

00:18:25.917 --> 00:18:28.125
-[GIRL 1] Huh?
-[GIRL 2] Wh-what?!

00:18:28.167 --> 00:18:31.125
[KAZUMA cackling]

00:18:31.167 --> 00:18:33.375
-[BOTH whimpering]
-[KAZUMA] Here we go, ladies!

00:18:33.417 --> 00:18:35.375
[cackling]

00:18:35.417 --> 00:18:37.667
[BOTH whimpering]

00:18:37.708 --> 00:18:40.583
[KAZUM] Yeah, I can feel
the steal comin' on!

00:18:40.625 --> 00:18:42.792
[BOTH whimpering]

00:18:42.833 --> 00:18:45.542
[BOTH]
No!

00:18:48.958 --> 00:18:49.917
I feel dirty.

00:18:50.958 --> 00:18:51.875
[MEGUMIN/DARKNESS/AQUA/KAZUMA]
KonoSuba

00:18:56.000 --> 00:18:58.083
What?!
It wasn't my fault!

00:18:58.125 --> 00:18:59.375
Why do you hate me?!

00:18:59.417 --> 00:19:01.583
Aqua sounds upset again.

00:19:01.625 --> 00:19:03.125
Wonder what happened
this time?

00:19:03.167 --> 00:19:04.833
I swear, it's like
she's only happy

00:19:04.875 --> 00:19:06.500
if she's causing
the biggest commotion!

00:19:10.167 --> 00:19:12.583
-[AQUA] I got my reward.
-Hmm?

00:19:12.625 --> 00:19:16.167
Guess why she only gave me
a hundred thousand eris?

00:19:16.208 --> 00:19:19.500
'Cause the cage is
two hundred thousand to fix.

00:19:19.542 --> 00:19:21.500
I didn't even break
the darn thing!

00:19:22.708 --> 00:19:23.750
That weasel!

00:19:23.792 --> 00:19:24.750
When I see him again,

00:19:24.792 --> 00:19:25.875
I'll hit him with God Blow

00:19:25.917 --> 00:19:27.875
right between the eyes!

00:19:27.917 --> 00:19:30.375
[KYOUYA]
There you are, Kazuma Satou!

00:19:30.417 --> 00:19:32.708
-[heavy breathing]
-[GIRLS whimpering]

00:19:32.750 --> 00:19:34.333
I happened to run
into a lady thief,

00:19:34.375 --> 00:19:36.167
and she told me
all about you.

00:19:36.208 --> 00:19:38.333
She said you steal panties!

00:19:38.375 --> 00:19:40.208
I also heard
a rumor going around

00:19:40.250 --> 00:19:43.125
about how you like
dousing women in slime.

00:19:43.167 --> 00:19:45.000
They call you
"Kazuma the Cad!"

00:19:45.042 --> 00:19:48.125
Who the hell's talkin'
about me behind my back!

00:19:48.167 --> 00:19:52.167
Lady Aqua, I swore to you that
I would defeat the Devil King.

00:19:52.208 --> 00:19:54.042
M'lady, please join my--

00:19:54.083 --> 00:19:56.250
God Blow!

00:19:56.292 --> 00:19:57.583
[KYOUYA screams]

00:19:57.625 --> 00:19:59.333
-[clattering]
-[ALL] Huh?

00:19:59.375 --> 00:20:01.667
-[GIRLS screaming]
-[KYOUYA groaning]

00:20:01.708 --> 00:20:02.667
[AQUA]
Come here!

00:20:02.708 --> 00:20:03.750
You broke the cage,

00:20:03.792 --> 00:20:05.708
and you're gonna pay
for it, or else!

00:20:05.750 --> 00:20:07.583
It cost three hundred thousand
to fix!

00:20:07.625 --> 00:20:10.292
Uh, yes, m'lady.
Uh, here!

00:20:10.333 --> 00:20:12.833
[KAZUMA] Wait, didn't she say
two hundred thou before?

00:20:12.875 --> 00:20:14.958
[AQUA]
Ohh, barkeep!

00:20:15.000 --> 00:20:18.167
One draft, please!
And a stack of fried frog, too!

00:20:20.417 --> 00:20:22.708
I-- Look, I know
you're the last person

00:20:22.750 --> 00:20:24.917
I should ask anything from.

00:20:24.958 --> 00:20:28.292
But I must!
Please, give me back my sword!

00:20:28.333 --> 00:20:29.458
If you do, I'll buy you

00:20:29.500 --> 00:20:30.833
the finest sword
in all the lan--

00:20:33.542 --> 00:20:35.875
Sorry. I hate to interrupt
your groveling,

00:20:35.917 --> 00:20:38.333
but he doesn't have
your sword anymore.

00:20:38.375 --> 00:20:39.375
Huh?

00:20:40.583 --> 00:20:42.667
[AQUA gulping]

00:20:42.708 --> 00:20:43.833
[exhales]

00:20:43.875 --> 00:20:47.417
Ha! That's very funny!
Come on now.

00:20:47.458 --> 00:20:49.833
Where is my magic sword,
really?

00:20:50.958 --> 00:20:52.167
I sold it.

00:20:52.208 --> 00:20:55.542
[KYOUYA]
Damn it!

00:20:55.583 --> 00:20:58.042
[BOTH]
Wait, Kyouya!

00:20:58.083 --> 00:21:00.083
[footsteps receding]

00:21:00.125 --> 00:21:01.625
Wish I could have got
more for it.

00:21:02.792 --> 00:21:05.208
That man has serious issues.

00:21:05.250 --> 00:21:06.500
Come to think of it,

00:21:06.542 --> 00:21:08.500
he called Aqua
a goddess a few times,

00:21:08.542 --> 00:21:10.792
and I was wondering
if you knew why that was.

00:21:13.083 --> 00:21:14.333
[KAZUMA]
The jig's up.

00:21:14.375 --> 00:21:16.708
It's time to tell her
and Megumin the truth.

00:21:18.375 --> 00:21:20.458
It was supposed
to be a secret.

00:21:20.500 --> 00:21:23.167
But I think
I can trust you with it.

00:21:23.208 --> 00:21:26.417
I am Aqua.
Worshipped by the Axis sect.

00:21:26.458 --> 00:21:28.167
The goddess of water.

00:21:28.208 --> 00:21:29.750
Sorry I couldn't
tell you sooner,

00:21:29.792 --> 00:21:31.750
but I am the goddess Aqua.

00:21:31.792 --> 00:21:33.750
[DARKNESS/MEGUMIN] You really
shouldn't drink so much.

00:21:33.792 --> 00:21:34.875
[AQUA]
I'm not drunk!

00:21:34.917 --> 00:21:36.542
[LUNA]
Emergency! Emergency!

00:21:36.583 --> 00:21:39.042
We need all adventurers
to arm themselves

00:21:39.083 --> 00:21:41.625
and rally at the main gate,
prepared for battle!

00:21:41.667 --> 00:21:43.792
Kazuma Satou,
you and your party

00:21:43.833 --> 00:21:45.375
in particular
are needed today,

00:21:45.417 --> 00:21:47.000
so please hurry!

00:21:47.042 --> 00:21:48.125
[ALL]
Huh?

00:21:48.167 --> 00:21:50.125
[PEOPLE murmuring]

00:21:58.542 --> 00:21:59.917
Uh-oh, him again.

00:22:01.125 --> 00:22:02.875
[DULLAHAN]
You wretches.

00:22:04.917 --> 00:22:06.750
What is wrong
with you people?!

00:22:06.792 --> 00:22:10.417
Why do you keep
bombarding my castle?!

00:22:12.458 --> 00:22:13.417
Say what?

00:23:44.500 --> 00:23:47.958
[AQUA] Day by day, Kazuma Satou
is growing stronger.

00:23:48.000 --> 00:23:49.542
His progress is going so well,

00:23:49.583 --> 00:23:51.542
he could defeat
the Devil King soon.

00:23:51.583 --> 00:23:53.833
Of course, this is all thanks
to my tal--

